Package: pipestreamr
Type: Package
Title: Non-blocking IO over stdin, stdout and stderr
Version: 1.0
Date: 2015-03-07
Author: Timothy H. Keitt, Jonathan Wakely
Maintainer: Timothy H. Keitt <tkeitt@gmail.com>
Description: This package allows you to write to stdin and read from stdout and stderr of a subprocess. It uses Jonathan Wakely's pstreams library. Reads are non-blocking. 
License: GPL (>= 2)
Imports:
  Rcpp (>= 0.11.0),
  methods
LinkingTo: Rcpp
